  ('audit_failure', 'Icon-only buttons in banner navigation (carousel controls, close buttons) lack ARIA labels', 'The BRANCY hero uses a Swiper.js carousel with navigation buttons. Carousel previous/next buttons are typically rendered as SVG arrows or CSS icons with no visible text label. Without an aria-label attribute, screen readers announce these as "button" with no description of the action. WCAG 4.1.2 requires all interactive elements to have an accessible name. Remediation: add `aria-label="Next slide"` / `aria-label="Previous slide"` to carousel navigation buttons. Similarly, any close button rendered as an ×  character must have `aria-label="Close"`. Lighthouse accessibility audit flags these as "Links do not have a discernible name" failures.', '{"applicable_when":"banner sections with carousel navigation, close buttons, or icon-only interactive elements","category":"w3c","evidence_source":"WCAG 2.1 SC 4.1.2; Drive corpus — BRANCY swiper carousel navigation 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[-0.021515794,0.0037684178,-0.020244163,-0.07215139,-0.055221085,0.0016958092,-0.011204493,0.0189252,-0.003569614,0.00715274,-0.009593848,0.012558765,-0.021352604,-0.00113963,0.13723603,-0.010177764,-0.020894712,-0.0017359154,-0.009064455,-0.0066327816,0.01780895,0.00013665635,-0.013816271,-0.024562689,0.012472581,0.0016128295,0.03723415,-0.015094023,0.004822107,0.0034456365,0.00929666,-0.007190717,0.043687202,-0.021567766,0.02538369,0.0167527,0.022388287,-0.020784747,-0.004585398,-0.0009090652,0.016857617,0.015762715,0.027017297,0.0070980373,-0.03353417,-0.006375121,1.3164517e-05,-0.009057338,-0.005799374,0.010605751,-0.028072862,0.0018314122,-0.0072105723,-0.16586244,0.012393211,-0.0073888856,-0.015104705,0.022897474,0.019030748,-0.004186883,-0.020933196,-0.01629003,0.00013985524,-0.044084415,0.015839495,-0.02328809,-0.002333888,0.0039711883,-0.02545076,0.0011590954,0.015648743,0.02011746,0.012356747,-0.01898163,0.0053650485,-0.018535245,0.01057523,-0.008982297,0.0009867401,0.0325