  ('best_practice', 'Avoid ''Learn More'' as the sole primary CTA on a conversion banner', 'Drunk Elephant uses "LEARN MORE" correctly: it is a secondary CTA that appears after the primary "SHOP ALL SKIN CARE". As a standalone primary CTA, "Learn More" signals to the user that no transaction is expected, which lowers purchase intent. When the goal is brand awareness or in-store consultation — as in Drunk Elephant''s consultation banner — "Learn More" is appropriate alongside a transactional "Book Now". For conversion campaigns, replace "Learn More" with a product- or offer-specific verb that names the destination: "Shop Lip Essentials", "Browse Skincare".', '{"applicable_when":"hero_main and promo_card banners with conversion goal","category":"cta","evidence_source":"Drive corpus — Drunk Elephant uses ''LEARN MORE'' as secondary, not primary 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[-0.01657318,-0.017940039,-2.9614189e-06,-0.074327454,-0.037085626,-0.013768047,-0.008015941,-0.00056024763,0.0044668294,-0.014871324,-0.0056506284,0.0063475515,-0.013960786,-0.02425162,0.12026719,0.0028865982,0.00024331993,0.0037514863,-0.0061851805,-0.008703207,-0.009128229,0.0069629955,-0.0044444525,-0.0061648493,-0.007933106,-0.019368712,0.016202109,0.010604429,0.02002923,-0.008012335,-0.009536806,-0.009213981,0.033035725,0.0056541916,0.008130602,0.043202832,0.047361717,-0.015164869,0.016377453,0.009915694,0.0037085435,0.036754366,0.0051245107,0.009772827,-0.026575241,-0.022066971,-0.008806325,-0.024945095,0.0019640587,0.029451078,-0.0029206616,0.019623024,-0.002113075,-0.15951048,-0.00087499816,0.0056411005,0.025137424,0.015117708,-0.002261302,-0.0029867403,-0.017092146,0.011512883,-0.01604126,-0.046831504,0.0031727506,-0.03737774,0.022561217,-0.02273328,-0.0006724001,-0.011801181,0.010394873,-0.012907586,-0.019505065,-0.016058587,-0.021285705,-0.0008047555,0.032090675,-0.013514746,-0.008869721,0.0043004085,0.01102141,-0.014237156,-0.011433292,0.00023845461,-0.020073416,0.0077872877,-0.03569669,0.0231432