  ('best_practice', 'CTA button must achieve 4.5:1 contrast ratio against its background', 'WCAG 1.4.3 requires 4.5:1 contrast for normal text and 3:1 for large text (18pt+ or 14pt bold). In the beauty corpus, the best-performing pattern is a dark button on a light background — the BRANCY hero uses a "btn-border-dark" class, giving black button text against a white or light background. Avoid placing a white CTA button directly over a light product background: the button disappears on mobile in partial sunlight. When the hero uses a full-bleed product image, add a semi-transparent scrim (rgba 0,0,0 / 0.35) behind the CTA button to guarantee contrast compliance.', '{"applicable_when":"all banner CTAs with a button container","category":"cta","evidence_source":"WCAG 2.1 SC 1.4.3; Drive corpus — BRANCY ''btn-border-dark'' pattern 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[-0.013050941,0.014537132,-0.019610709,-0.09932004,-0.032841984,-0.0053271777,-0.010410924,0.026224267,-0.019653264,-0.017417947,-0.025053743,0.006651304,-0.00507341,-0.003074911,0.12647834,0.017876714,-0.030822683,-0.017535679,-0.018464075,0.0060808538,0.024597734,0.005621871,-0.0149798095,-0.008647969,-0.0053121485,-0.022186039,0.029378202,0.013782567,0.026656859,0.011255064,-0.018935677,0.00070080254,0.028461423,-0.003835598,0.0033212923,0.04319148,0.021286739,-0.028138496,0.036834978,0.01207299,0.0094689,0.010080926,0.01742535,-0.0045827306,-0.018574968,-0.008773941,-0.007894009,-0.017027203,0.023805616,0.015906122,-0.017143106,0.016469494,-0.016867178,-0.15700892,0.010211779,0.0040513766,-0.015679933,0.010293954,0.011078162,-0.012042798,0.003518099,0.027414797,0.013989774,-0.06626474,-0.0057262755,-0.042147037,-0.0017501585,-0.007977718,-0.012464562,-0.0008104269,0.0107616875,0.0139931,-0.028812474,-0.024623748,0.017543772,-0.014297237,-0.009091457,-0.004772482,0.0032225673,0.023063298,0.010028306,-0.022416065,0.0027496628,-0.0075203483,-0.0045289802,-0.023422208,-0.002970733,-0.007893646,0.011969561,-0.0046949456,0.019