  ('best_practice', 'CTA buttons must be at least 44×44px on mobile to meet touch target accessibility requirements', 'WCAG 2.5.5 and Apple''s Human Interface Guidelines both specify minimum 44×44px touch targets. Salon booking banners with "BOOKING APPOINTMENT" CTAs are high-risk for this failure because appointment links are often styled as text-only anchors without explicit padding. Set minimum `min-height: 44px; padding: 12px 24px` on all CTA anchor tags in Shopify sections. Undersized targets cause accidental misses on thumbs, reduce conversion, and fail automated Lighthouse accessibility audits — which in the banner agent pipeline triggers a performance-audit node retry.', '{"applicable_when":"all banner CTAs rendered on mobile viewports","category":"mobile","evidence_source":"WCAG 2.5.5; Apple HIG; Drive corpus — salon booking CTAs 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[-0.02030818,-0.016506486,-0.012590012,-0.06765742,-0.031261835,-0.008361356,-0.0065427828,-0.013350034,0.0041445848,0.0096433265,-0.027943676,0.015248153,-0.008004713,-0.0074334946,0.14380358,0.001463604,-0.03421339,0.0013354947,-0.02871298,-0.0076506394,-0.014372555,0.003301126,-0.020481102,-0.027434282,0.02669076,-0.017701631,0.0291885,0.00576857,0.0276864,-0.0019517267,-0.009812234,-0.01857483,0.02741971,0.015475906,0.015230845,0.02953659,0.020347944,-0.01599249,0.014345885,0.01579791,0.017801516,-0.006304717,0.014021025,0.018132953,-0.016084628,0.0045044934,0.006899264,-0.042618357,-0.016221082,0.02934338,-0.004338719,0.018334774,-0.01645649,-0.15974842,0.0042345994,0.0051202285,-0.01280518,0.035235938,-0.030916762,-0.004539623,-0.0052839066,0.029316932,0.006794096,-0.05633634,-0.0122840945,-0.018995758,-0.0009980211,-0.0074613234,-0.028234856,0.009274471,-0.0013319283,0.0005282765,-0.005685044,-0.017137075,-0.00013405384,-0.010895857,-0.014656402,0.013911004,-0.0026652608,0.015413764,0.011792158,-0.0046979566,-0.019117426,0.0025268663,-0.012951973,-0.02599185,-0.0023507678,-0.0032398095,0.008829136,0.00431