  ('best_practice', 'Hero banners convert best with one message, one proof point, and one CTA', 'Every high-performing banner in the beauty corpus leads with a single benefit statement ("Glow Beyond Beauty", "Nourishing Soap"), supports it with one descriptive line, and closes with exactly one CTA button. Banners that introduce competing promotions — sale badge + new arrival + CTA — lose click-through focus across beauty verticals. Reserve the hero area for a single offer or brand message and move secondary promotions to promo cards or announcement bars.', '{"applicable_when":"all hero and collection banners","category":"hierarchy","evidence_source":"Drive corpus — Bearen, NaturaGlow, Kylie Jenner banners 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[-0.025205202,0.003994187,0.015902998,-0.08108475,-0.011270359,-0.007153074,-0.00800926,0.026374009,0.0016159505,-0.013656333,-0.008549432,-0.0045559355,0.0076273014,-0.02373285,0.12032451,0.01953064,-0.0047715814,-0.017732767,-0.005382629,0.009103177,0.000776383,0.017815456,-0.03640302,-0.010432377,-0.00095334643,-0.0060349344,0.0316334,0.0022831515,0.009031449,0.0074454877,-0.010901708,0.011579943,0.035390966,0.007843403,0.011096448,0.0280908,0.024381034,-0.0026954266,0.015639896,0.03278829,0.014676901,0.0123319635,0.0068384428,-0.00401822,-0.013872784,-0.022035535,0.0037263136,-0.023043886,0.007240507,0.04321458,-0.031893205,0.035762258,-0.0065011154,-0.15455216,-0.00912339,-0.005107084,-0.010182177,-0.005308054,0.005635006,-0.013721131,-0.00956027,0.0151493,0.00062769384,-0.049207218,0.0012281459,-0.028419983,0.005556913,-0.029992614,-0.016020305,-0.010786054,0.00893639,-0.012013121,-0.009731201,-0.013030267,0.027551275,-0.008364776,0.015780855,-0.0030186272,-0.01400721,0.015718428,0.018944424,-0.025573866,-0.03963858,-0.0005558964,-0.009322517,-0.017826786,-0.021692803,0.028447589,0.014367768,0.014819592,0.02718266,0.013721008,-0.0061887386,-0.025136149,0.005081507,-0.010801476,0.0015815385,0.014501708,-0.022095554,-0.02165944,-0.02774944,0