  ('best_practice', 'Limited-edition labelling in the headline creates scarcity urgency without discounting', 'Kylie Jenner''s lip product launch uses "limited-edition" in supporting copy and "NOW AVAILABLE" as the launch badge — creating urgency through exclusivity rather than price. Scarcity language ("limited-edition", "exclusive", "only while stocks last") maintains brand price integrity while motivating purchase action. Combine scarcity copy with a product-specific CTA ("shop now" pointing to the product PDP) rather than a generic collection CTA, to reduce friction between the urgency signal and the purchase action. For Shopify implementation, connect the banner to a product metafield that auto-removes the "limited-edition" badge when inventory falls to zero.', '{"applicable_when":"product launch banners for beauty, fashion, and lifestyle","category":"urgency","evidence_source":"Drive corpus — Kylie Jenner Cosmetics ''limited-edition formulas'', ''NOW AVAILABLE'' 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[-0.0066028587,-0.0012201492,0.02211871,-0.08362717,0.0061403797,-0.007828018,-0.013073531,-0.0047760378,-0.0056793955,-0.0067316843,-0.009852221,-0.009621108,-0.01049536,-0.0070133563,0.13547534,0.00961911,0.004874461,-0.010059794,0.015785161,0.023893083,-0.015953543,0.016653366,-0.0010823924,-0.012297348,0.0013369141,-0.011218495,0.02612595,-0.005663866,0.014064998,0.039644383,-0.040459793,1.710854e-05,0.027074143,-0.007030955,0.01984496,0.0057830866,0.03106629,-0.013970726,0.017518722,0.013115974,0.021690615,0.03716886,0.024743518,-0.018632976,-0.018042572,0.004833637,-0.013872519,-0.021301517,0.008332647,5.3238724e-05,-0.027414167,0.0070752325,-0.0041607954,-0.1510362,-0.0078114136,-0.017641831,0.0049927277,0.014378592,0.007858958,-0.023993911,-0.028191973,0.026539044,0.01100638,-0.03733448,0.018893804,0.003360715,0.0007879488,0.010200722,-0.006134593,-0.007351103,0.02353199,-0.008791697,0.017940432,-0.00060628774,0.011091316,-0.029177535,0.006343677,-0.0014240015,-0.028763477,0