  ('best_practice', 'Luxury beauty copy uses short declarative statements and avoids all discount and promotional language', 'WESSAINT AURENT: "we believe that beauty is more than just skin deep. It''s a feeling of confidence, a reflection of self-care, and an expression." — short declarative sentences with no discount language, price points, or promotional frames. Drunk Elephant frames its identity as "performance and personality can live in the same jar" — a statement of philosophy, not a product claim. Luxury banners earn trust through conviction of voice: introduce no urgency language, no percentages, and no sale badges in the hero area. The CTA on luxury banners is always a discovery verb — "DISCOVER MORE" or "LEARN MORE" — not a transaction verb like "Buy Now."', '{"applicable_when":"premium and luxury brand hero banners","category":"brand","evidence_source":"Drive corpus — WESSAINT AURENT ''beauty is more than just skin deep'', Drunk Elephant philosophy copy 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[-0.031940397,-0.0110302605,0.00011510144,-0.08663833,-0.02479371,-0.008828882,-0.007651309,-0.013978049,0.004271645,-0.012269626,-0.0024782342,0.016738936,-0.0052724644,-0.034334566,0.13683823,0.01462574,-0.0056668515,0.007071752,0.008295458,0.0021107665,0.0060216286,-0.012791388,-0.008279111,-0.009890953,-0.0010830442,-0.003448488,0.0051368237,0.0206988,0.01596621,-0.004118086,-0.00981332,-0.0045836167,0.02580302,0.02113293,0.03569248,0.038206182,0.036987033,-0.022382405,0.016401904,0.013563158,0.004063169,0.0049874024,0.023021027,-0.0021546045,-0.010311127,0.007236736,-0.0020355838,-0.03050643,-0.0035776305,0.03271077,-0.019570539,0.00515965,-0.0103787705,-0.15018846,0.0051743635,-9.964282e-05,0.01191434,0.017524105,0.007891369,-0.0069477367,-0.027788851,0.017422477,-0.021558255,-0.045203425,0.022265567,-0.027980313,0.0020842564,-0.026225017,0.010151675,-0.0023767508,-0.0052189226,-0.0006404577,0.005267823,-0.017004538,0.008817315,-0.013402844,0.01633746,-0.009251453,0.010180456,-0.