  ('best_practice', 'Name the specific product or collection in the banner copy, not just the category', 'NaturaGlow names the product twice: "Nourishing Soap" as the headline and "NaturaGlow Body Wash" as the product name in the copy. Kylie Jenner names the product in supporting copy: "coconut water lip stain delivers lasting comfort and up to 24-hour moisture." The bath salts banner includes the full product composition — "BERGAMOT & YLANG YLANG BATH SALTS 300g." Specific product names improve click quality: the shopper arrives at the PDP already knowing what they are buying, which reduces bounce rate. Avoid "our bestselling cream" or "new collection" — these phrases are interchangeable across every beauty brand.', '{"applicable_when":"product and collection banners with a specific SKU or collection","category":"catalog","evidence_source":"Drive corpus — ''NaturaGlow Body Wash'', ''Coconut Water Lip Stain'', ''BERGAMOT & YLANG YLANG Bath Salts'' 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[-0.01648613,0.013011152,0.008720882,-0.082808174,-0.021791818,-0.00820477,-0.015036018,0.015087767,-0.005875634,-0.037427664,-0.017966835,-0.001805647,0.013310862,-0.016513579,0.11383799,0.012180796,-0.00093972095,-0.0013624035,-0.008231228,0.0051469547,-0.007550102,-4.467394e-05,0.0010770471,-0.02565176,-0.0061857942,0.009491984,0.0124509465,0.0128067145,0.01360862,0.014823642,-0.032997906,0.0027797837,0.04559031,0.0056101703,0.024814459,0.04437575,0.015743893,-0.017707583,0.0040402114,0.028131407,-0.005307632,0.018431142,0.017091189,-0.024623146,0.0015385504,0.0069698105,0.0041017593,-0.0047807856,0.00922646,0.044665493,-0.013806629,0.016118858,-0.022799397,-0.15454087,-0.018182762,-0.016958375,-0.0064902892,0.0073296893,-0.009992846,0.00053796556,-0.009916801,0.024421798,-0.018629324,-0.04217084,-0.00403488,-0.031639546,-0.0010151241,-0.02029916,-0.010764473,0.0046100016,0.014507473,-0.0013155488,-0.02570558,-0.0036931045,-0.0090982625,-0.038340043,0.0270536,-0.00034290954,-0.034725662,0.024850085,0