  ('best_practice', 'Place the percentage discount in the headline rather than in the description', 'Both Nature''s Touch ("Get 25% Off All Cosmetic Creams") and Botanical Republic ("Get Discount Up To 25%") surface the discount percentage as the headline. Burying the discount in the body copy — "Enjoy 25% off today" — reduces offer salience for users who scan rather than read. When the offer includes a range ("Up To 25%"), place the range in the headline. When the discount is fixed, lead with the specific number: "25% Off" performs better than "Up to a quarter off" because numbers are processed faster than written approximations.', '{"applicable_when":"discount-led promotional banners","category":"urgency","evidence_source":"Drive corpus — Nature''s Touch ''Get 25% Off All Cosmetic Creams'', Botanical Republic ''Get Discount Up To 25%'' 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[0.004948918,-0.014385633,-0.0023968725,-0.067901604,-0.03519782,0.008604182,0.0035373438,0.019235818,-0.018949645,0.011214275,-0.019198261,0.010184446,0.0012024381,-0.031371966,0.11917063,0.021449696,0.012579152,-0.019750822,-0.0037003271,-0.0006004762,0.013075906,0.029194107,-0.015592503,-0.004063259,-0.018317072,0.0009906588,0.0063533224,-0.0017487805,0.019445095,0.03538679,-0.007861203,-0.0130946925,0.041807324,-3.466831e-05,0.012480076,0.027943872,0.033950742,-0.0009482582,0.0058095325,0.014237684,0.019108525,-0.010584019,0.0059800814,0.008772059,-0.004461172,0.009959765,-0.024623308,-0.02889739,0.026143925,0.040057525,-0.013378684,0.011642839,-0.0006102465,-0.16754885,-0.010068222,-0.018848643,0.0013730214,0.010332687,0.009577756,-0.009379207,-0.0030979782,0.0061193923,-0.017010039,-0.0100728795,-0.006084879,-0.012277713,0.0026476465,-0.011572512,-0.03092919,0.008588587,0.036562026,0.0102243265,0.006331496,-0.015894469,0.012717485,-0.027999768,0.016705127,-0.0013246106,-0.016814271,0.013301373,-0.007762407,-0.007798167,-0.03838466,0.009680572,0.0010599932,-0.0030933307,-0.010663402,0.00053740304,-0.00160687