  ('best_practice', 'Show the product in its use context rather than isolated on white to increase purchase intent', 'The bath salts banner uses the product in context — "BERGAMOT & YLANG YLANG BATH SALTS 300g with plastic scoop" — surrounded by natural ingredients rather than as a plain pack shot on white. NaturaGlow Body Wash shows the bottle in a styled bathroom setting. Bearen pairs its product with a lifestyle glow visual. In-context imagery increases purchase intent by helping the shopper visualise product use and reduces the visual gap between ad and ownership. For beauty products, in-context means the product beside a textured surface, held by a hand, or alongside complementary ingredients — not floating on a white background.', '{"applicable_when":"product and collection banners for beauty, bath, and body categories","category":"layout","evidence_source":"Drive corpus — Bath Salts ''with plastic scoop'', NaturaGlow soap in bathroom setting, Bearen lifestyle 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[-0.009186085,0.0131844785,-0.0009883024,-0.09572979,-0.013927651,0.004746577,0.0032816927,0.023949228,-0.015169635,-0.006990123,-0.0031868676,-7.4724056e-05,0.0004932509,-0.0027204242,0.120683216,0.01866462,-0.010353999,0.0037850144,0.017870534,-0.00795143,-0.0033995945,0.006917845,0.0034384308,-0.007831273,0.011558763,0.003826519,0.0015399571,-0.0024654078,0.016697591,0.01919365,-0.017995235,0.023167305,0.042329844,0.007293546,0.017159928,0.0331381,0.002824701,-0.04015141,0.01216976,0.035434224,-0.01820913,0.014278,0.010031277,-0.017873675,-0.011689752,0.0062011825,0.028321628,-0.012460241,0.021740634,-0.0015850986,0.0036283375,0.029196804,-0.004799916,-0.14090604,-0.014810343,-0.016757146,-0.0050326246,-0.0033956415,-0.005777414,-0.0061930427,-0.005783221,0.021030817,0.0012390122,-0.046001773,-0.0146146845,-0.029579831,-0.013927231,-0.015781928,0.006924498,0.013860381,0.009414315,0.008290043,-0.005556092,0.018058054,0.01972077,-0.017893882,-0.003069781,-0.01243831,-0.019123215,0.02