  ('best_practice', 'Social proof numbers visible in the hero increase trust on discovery banners for cold audiences', 'The skincare brand surfaces two proof points directly in the hero: "400+ New Collection" and "10k+ Satisfied Customer." The cruelty-free brand testimonial — "''I''m so happy to find a cruelty-free brand that actually works. My skin feels soft and hydrated!'' — Nusrat Jahan, Product designer" — adds credibility via a named reviewer with a job title. Social proof in the hero is most effective for cold audiences with no prior brand exposure. For warm audiences (retargeting), replace proof metrics with product-specific copy — they already trust the brand and need a reason to return, not validation.', '{"applicable_when":"hero banners for new visitor acquisition and brand awareness","category":"catalog","evidence_source":"Drive corpus — skincare brand ''10k+ Satisfied Customer'', cruelty-free brand testimonial ''Nusrat Jahan'' 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[-0.02576517,-0.012104885,0.00792611,-0.0742576,-0.0048513757,-0.005304934,-0.039497282,-0.0014785952,-0.031497557,-0.009314694,0.020937897,-0.007845515,0.0084362365,-0.0013755176,0.12957498,0.045057893,0.012223609,-0.0044469116,0.019179868,-0.02157119,-0.0146324355,0.01035963,-0.0207292,-0.014316547,-0.008740647,0.0030772132,0.0132603,0.012350175,0.0014374468,0.031948365,-0.008752498,0.004074648,0.021379359,0.0042446954,0.01924977,0.02356785,0.021163704,-0.032189347,-0.006063455,0.026919432,0.011541551,0.0155547485,0.015581011,-0.0019466047,-0.025918625,0.013544711,0.014828865,-0.04634452,0.021414518,0.037421297,-0.0049600094,-0.0099457465,-0.00410784,-0.14623533,-0.012923525,-0.017242651,-0.0038903381,0.005121179,0.00328361,0.0026263134,-0.021076968,0.041113116,-0.005683983,-0.06318381,0.009874716,-0.034814518,0.03514609,-0.02874235,-0.0041505108,-0.0025367355,0.011396367,0.0062859096,0.007992531,-0.011579584,0.02745149,-0.039932977,0.0057816673,-0.012719847,-0.0015869905,0.021801872,0.018091327,-0.016650874,