  ('best_practice', 'Start CTAs with an action verb — Shop, Explore, Discover, Buy, or Book', 'Every high-intent CTA in the corpus opens with a verb: "Shop", "Explore", "Discover", "Buy", "Book", "Browse". Noun-led CTAs such as "New Collection" or "25% Off" communicate information rather than directing an action, resulting in lower click-through. Verb capitalisation style should match brand tone — Kylie Jenner uses all-lowercase "shop now", Drunk Elephant uses all-caps "SHOP ALL SKIN CARE", and natural beauty brands like Bearen prefer title case "Explore Collection". Maintain consistent capitalisation style across all banners for the same brand.', '{"applicable_when":"all banner CTAs","category":"cta","evidence_source":"Drive corpus — Kylie Jenner ''shop now'', Drunk Elephant ''SHOP ALL SKIN CARE'', NaturaGlow ''BUY NOW'', Bearen ''Explore Collection'' 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[-0.025897998,-0.0028322695,-0.00043224098,-0.0616761,-0.014616353,-0.004485996,-0.021828985,0.013907253,-0.01142047,-0.006864958,-0.028182428,0.0008213087,-0.009131054,-0.01064161,0.13204959,0.0066344664,-0.01647975,-3.635406e-05,-0.018142646,-0.02500222,-0.010742749,0.022036478,-0.0052541527,-0.021259423,0.00200311,-0.019096749,0.027084446,0.017334726,0.01578717,0.0041005267,-0.02715422,0.017264875,0.040969957,0.0001631127,0.0027609286,0.036911204,0.01152329,0.007571527,0.008798967,0.028416423,-0.0017500258,0.0021744356,-0.004797227,-0.0112021165,-0.0076570613,0.022541456,0.019067772,-0.02949658,0.007485468,0.038651586,-0.020982483,0.017667968,-0.009252908,-0.15171121,0.009630233,-0.015814872,0.0026946021,0.013214234,0.016136874,-0.0020682795,-0.0061742803,0.02634188,-0.024475658,-0.05258698,0.012574015,-0.041049443,0.012167583,-0.011210782,-0.022513893,-0.027055498,0.009785854,-0.012574582,-0.008925645,-0.042999707,0.013834841,0.00044504835,0.02533443,-0.020438181,-0.012448984,0.021893347,0.01021285,-0.018855393,-0.04297883,0.012129866,-0.024417879,-0.012895292,-0.0048096306,0.006028315,0.003200