  ('best_practice', 'Supporting copy in a hero banner should be two lines maximum at desktop sizes', 'All strong-performing banners in the beauty corpus keep supporting copy to 2 lines at 16–18px: "Clean, cruelty-free, and glow-boosting products for every shade of beauty." Longer descriptions belong on PDP or About sections — placing them in the hero competes with the CTA and forces text reflow on mobile. If the brand story requires more words, use an About Us section banner with a "Discover More" CTA (as WESSAINT AURENT does) rather than expanding hero copy beyond two lines.', '{"applicable_when":"hero_main, collection_header placements","category":"hierarchy","evidence_source":"Drive corpus — beauty banner audit 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[-0.0023909274,-0.0029753495,-0.00920764,-0.07919944,-0.0125723425,-0.02193131,-0.016926596,-0.008189445,0.0052361083,-0.020227715,-0.0038491997,0.0038786745,0.0020715122,-0.0034940362,0.14049466,0.019866267,-0.00994543,-0.009631705,-0.0014798511,0.0043296046,0.00031558264,-0.0024341831,-0.017130403,-0.013917105,-0.015885096,8.713443e-05,0.01052797,0.02455264,0.028216567,-0.003940895,-0.021593174,-0.015301483,0.05057337,-0.0131287,0.017137287,0.04286836,0.026741277,-0.03293559,0.0037631379,0.024198828,0.008505238,0.010958019,0.031688944,-0.00910423,-0.02175496,0.0056453394,-0.0025327227,-0.037302006,0.01668952,0.062068477,-0.02911286,-0.00034567702,0.0050962316,-0.15285027,-0.02009615,-0.004080823,0.0026623134,0.028161362,0.00047688084,-0.005254379,0.0013908894,0.01624762,0.005667945,-0.057063673,0.0018863733,-0.033278026,0.0075294976,-0.02668664,0.010631625,0.014082388,-0.00074408366,-0.020351028,-0.012500103,-0.012997708,0.0035836052,-0.032787316,0.018021595,0.0040619913,0.0036172944,0.022376878,0.01948464,-0.00033166,-0.022756997,-0.0067862254,-0.01731989,0.0016282717,-0.020875083,0.01630088,0.026179407,-0.00067563506,0.028338512,0.02170679,0.020442175,-0.004237911,0.0028450808,-0.016631426,0.011663646,0.01502959,-0.011612942,-0.0154