  ('best_practice', 'Surface the discount or price point in the headline when running a promotional campaign', 'When a discount is available, it is the primary reason to click — place the percentage in the headline. "Get 25% Off All Cosmetic Creams" (Nature''s Touch) and "Get Discount Up To 25%" (Botanical Republic) work because the number and product category appear together, answering two key shopper questions: how much, and on what. Body copy handles the reassurance narrative: "Pamper your skin with our nourishing cosmetic creams — crafted for radiant, silky-smooth results." Discount banners without a visible percentage in the headline perform measurably below category benchmarks for beauty ecommerce.', '{"applicable_when":"promotional banners with price reduction offer","category":"catalog","evidence_source":"Drive corpus — Nature''s Touch ''25% Off All Cosmetic Creams'', Botanical Republic ''Get Discount Up To 25%'' 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[-0.00986749,-0.0010797991,0.0013677177,-0.064993665,-0.041753948,0.0037121954,-0.013086077,0.002657579,-0.012373797,-0.011299626,-0.013574505,0.0056044604,0.024623878,-0.028313091,0.11816911,0.028326366,0.014191054,-0.022085018,-0.0035593996,-0.0029057364,-0.00048367964,0.019782044,-0.016552057,-0.017565133,-0.003764119,0.0033861229,-0.004836267,0.001803752,0.017479055,0.028547175,-0.019958233,-0.0018923869,0.04808809,-0.003350535,0.026893724,0.03363987,0.011611148,-0.0019839609,0.021884192,0.034827594,0.022478364,0.0016502546,0.002164051,-0.0067148036,0.00026616856,0.003979072,-0.014735511,-0.026869355,0.022937652,0.05009987,-0.022454891,0.013534039,0.0025740825,-0.16834341,-0.000847834,-0.006855904,-0.009983164,0.01594788,-0.006723609,-0.016360527,-0.006521482,0.015459014,-0.0038631682,-0.042158447,0.0062015136,-0.023640215,-0.0016535782,-0.014302063,-0.017610995,-0.014277557,0.03062346,-0.0023339104,-0.020718839,-0.016573025,0.023053378,-0.007490597,0.008706905,-0.013115173,-0.02678889,0.008976837,-0.012374448,-0.0061623296,-