  ('best_practice', 'The CTA button must be visible above the fold on a 390×844 mobile screen without scrolling', 'On a 390×844 iPhone 14 viewport with a standard Shopify header (~56px), the visible hero area is approximately 390×788px. The CTA must appear within this area. Stacked layouts that push the product image full-height above the fold and place the headline and CTA below will lose the majority of mobile impressions from users who do not scroll. Limit product image height to 60% of mobile viewport height (~470px) and place the headline + CTA within the remaining 40% (~318px). The Bearen and NaturaGlow banners both keep copy and CTA above the 788px threshold.', '{"applicable_when":"hero_main banners, all Shopify storefronts","category":"mobile","evidence_source":"Drive corpus — beauty hero banners; iPhone 14 390×844 standard viewport 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[0.0007069512,0.011671815,-0.0013501069,-0.09410516,-0.02490198,-0.003973821,-0.025914641,0.0018740406,-0.003511753,-0.0054112263,-0.028623886,0.002323984,0.0058641443,-0.026016396,0.11140074,0.034139335,-0.02821186,-0.012707443,0.000970251,0.0027442588,-0.0030520132,0.004207529,0.0025988333,-0.0022191058,0.0027964949,0.0016499072,0.009017515,0.015946079,0.022259604,0.034301054,-0.03309277,-0.010394491,0.012835808,-0.0087361215,-0.011202386,0.035382405,0.04210879,-0.025944868,0.0076551843,0.024439508,0.028733445,0.014592095,0.0064067007,0.008024056,-0.025192102,-0.0009121578,0.012059365,-0.028170213,0.008922292,0.041846056,-0.03545141,0.01206146,-0.01754936,-0.15509412,-0.023471791,0.004422293,-0.010092904,0.011077774,-0.0047774552,-0.015806817,0.006556151,0.03407837,0.012204368,-0.059720013,0.0032160983,-0.027134007,-0.0031570985,-0.014599614,-0.015958274,0.017703708,-0.015064364,0.006234713,-0.0017931275,-0.009228204,0.009820726,-0.022044528,0.0045886966,0.0148011325,-0.004051173,0.028122764,0.006627739,0.0075216745,-0.01691123,-0.000513891,-0.0022968673,-0.0039460678,-0.006250359,0.006302096,-0.020987304,0.