  ('best_practice', 'Time-bound urgency copy (''This Weekend Only'', ''Today Only'') lifts conversion within the offer window', 'The flash sale banner demonstrates the correct urgency pattern: a bold "FLASH SALE" badge paired with the time constraint "THIS WEEKEND ONLY" communicates both the magnitude and the deadline of the offer in two lines. Generic banners without a time bound ("Big Savings") underperform against time-anchored copy. The time constraint must appear in the headline or immediately below it — not in the footer or disclaimer — so it is visible above the fold without scrolling. After the offer window closes, swap the urgency headline for the standard brand message to avoid confusing returning visitors with an expired promotion.', '{"applicable_when":"promotional banners with time-limited offers","category":"urgency","evidence_source":"Drive corpus — ''FLASH SALE / THIS WEEKEND ONLY'' template 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[0.0007350032,0.01641131,-0.009066092,-0.05827702,-0.0035064565,0.0047771945,0.011350077,-0.010785986,-0.006492608,-0.007953036,-0.021874456,0.0076115187,-0.0019951009,-0.023825815,0.10661932,0.037848253,-0.0076630577,-0.0010133731,0.0069369245,0.009344128,0.0010810813,0.018947316,-0.009180373,-0.010861136,0.01734677,0.0016200276,0.005952337,0.0080885505,0.029588096,0.04636289,-0.0070855385,0.007594253,0.041959945,-0.012359507,-0.003618952,0.0054348363,0.016113726,-0.023666505,0.003743862,0.018923834,-0.01084275,0.01846946,0.011553146,-0.0011439951,-0.0069530914,0.0049347766,0.006022397,-0.0060558417,-0.0030022154,0.041464828,-0.014811507,0.017329566,-0.009869409,-0.17869002,-0.0044161943,-0.021091761,0.007527333,-0.010702788,0.021161688,-0.0070523224,-0.008455696,0.010726424,0.008245769,-0.05007211,0.021723067,-0.008954931,-0.0127176335,0.0154796215,-0.037891414,0.008743514,0.022942368,-0.023235178,-0.0044781445,-0.01429274,0.030097209,-0.01595344,0.030277712,-0.0034534766,-0.017889474,0.0045581134,-0.00065751077,-0.011412337,-0.01330882,-0.0