  ('best_practice', 'Use discovery CTAs (''Explore Collection'', ''Shop Our Collection'') for catalog-wide banners, not ''Buy Now''', 'Bearen uses "Explore Collection", the eco skincare brand uses "Shop Our Collection", and the skincare essentials brand uses "Explore Now →" — all discovery-framed CTAs that invite browsing rather than demanding a transaction. "Buy Now" is appropriate when the banner links to a single product PDP; on collection pages it creates a mismatch between the CTA promise and the destination (a grid, not a buy button), increasing bounce. Use "Explore" or "Shop" for collection destinations and "Shop [Product Name]" for product-level hero destinations.', '{"applicable_when":"collection_header and homepage catalog section banners","category":"catalog","evidence_source":"Drive corpus — Bearen ''Explore Collection'', eco skincare ''Shop Our Collection'', skincare brand ''Explore Now →'' 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[-0.027739307,-0.012242999,-0.005534638,-0.07674145,-0.01502807,-0.02385701,0.0016616256,-0.0071045794,0.005896728,-0.006691663,-0.005530949,0.0030742423,0.0076803984,0.003134122,0.12464818,0.0020914674,0.018568382,-0.011051073,-0.005891153,-0.004848326,-0.009789474,0.01214663,-0.0029385686,-0.0002963658,-0.0031831178,-0.028095258,0.019127721,0.0012209945,0.026444716,0.002667802,-0.0066466583,0.005230383,0.02888619,-0.011208831,0.008550622,0.024746029,0.014671623,-0.003276229,-0.0138590215,0.033249598,0.00876632,0.014568661,0.011284712,0.0019554258,-0.02269977,-0.010519034,-0.0006451125,-0.01571365,-0.014616926,0.039269827,-0.02499884,0.02566278,-0.0016712444,-0.15566207,-0.012554323,-0.014597275,-0.005050267,0.023911703,0.0059808637,-0.02374667,-0.015795378,0.029291645,-0.03900125,-0.051022872,0.024617326,-0.032704674,0.012795249,-0.015033545,-0.012205887,0.0027510386,0.011309976,-0.0059770006,-0.0044821654,-0.02672357,0.02045132,-0.0019766288,0.011127948,-0.01243484,-0.0137564195,0.048161473,0.027535142,-0.012895517,-0.02498207,0.005760717,-0.01