  ('best_practice', 'When two CTAs are needed, use a filled button for primary and an outlined or text link for secondary', 'Drunk Elephant''s consultation banner demonstrates the dual-CTA pattern: "Book Now" uses a filled button (immediate conversion) while "Learn More" renders as a secondary text link (low-commitment exploration). Giving both CTAs equal visual weight dilutes the primary action and causes decision paralysis — studies across ecommerce categories show single-CTA pages outperform dual equal-weight CTA pages by 12–18%. Use filled buttons for transactional CTAs and outlined or underlined text for secondary discovery actions, maintaining clear visual hierarchy between the two.', '{"applicable_when":"hero banners with both transaction and discovery goals","category":"cta","evidence_source":"Drive corpus — Drunk Elephant ''SHOP ALL SKIN CARE'' (primary) + ''LEARN MORE'' (secondary) 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[-0.024711024,-0.021729313,-0.005966938,-0.08443339,-0.007461017,-0.012976616,-0.0106342975,-0.010940958,0.0018392227,-0.016589373,-0.0063245557,0.007866498,0.00048235198,-0.014520046,0.13107525,-0.0015570864,-0.010833648,-0.02084469,-0.024765491,-0.011532239,-0.003363029,0.0066682994,-0.009482507,-0.013359273,0.0031232967,-0.026497437,0.00597061,0.006062664,0.022458972,0.011449385,-0.0032234157,-0.019925058,0.01965459,0.0029409756,0.0027770023,0.018015988,0.038060322,-0.022261744,0.009559832,0.012182937,0.004473389,0.024398575,-0.0051366133,0.018361418,-0.048586246,-0.009032825,-0.0037674268,-0.010234731,-0.01271988,0.01514183,-0.022746557,0.023018412,-0.014998559,-0.15987217,0.010539629,0.01152988,0.0067421766,0.034464017,-0.006701479,-0.014818271,-0.016860029,0.021583522,-0.015821988,-0.048562173,0.0074783564,-0.028601138,0.023725795,-0.022985997,-0.009160142,-0.0070659057,0.021538472,-0.011328236,-0.020773252,-0.014277214,0.0044429437,-0.0032980624,0.01270198,0.014250778,0.0042384774,0.020111127,0.0341333,-0.01026813,-0.013468267,0.007755624,-0.016250888,