  ('brand_example', 'Clean beauty brand voice — benefit-glow tone with inclusivity (Bearen pattern)', 'Bearen''s hero banner: headline "Glow Beyond Beauty", subheadline "Beauty That Shines Naturally", body copy "Clean, cruelty-free, and glow-boosting products for every shade of beauty.", CTA "Explore Collection". This voice archetype is characterised by aspiration with inclusivity ("every shade of beauty"), nature-derived language ("glow", "clean", "shines"), and absence of clinical or discount language. The CTA is discovery-oriented and low-pressure. Tone rhythm uses short declarative fragments — "Glow Beyond Beauty" is three words, not a full sentence — which creates visual impact at large type sizes without the copy feeling dense. Use this pattern for hero banners targeting millennial and Gen Z audiences in the natural beauty segment on brand awareness or new customer acquisition campaigns.', '{"applicable_when":"natural, cruelty-free, clean beauty brand awareness campaigns","category":"clean_beauty","evidence_source":"Drive corpus — Bearen hero banners 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[-0.016344626,0.006529132,0.0028125383,-0.07423164,-0.025346769,-0.015999,-0.0010870005,-0.0048029646,-0.005615948,0.0041176286,-0.0071345447,0.0015788146,0.004675093,0.006536355,0.13095298,-0.0013408782,-0.009121183,0.007905437,0.004835761,0.0015148546,-0.015027177,0.0012247678,-0.00852461,-0.01316129,-0.017850952,-0.0125833545,0.020145914,0.0164583,0.034293376,-0.0011600873,0.0019583027,0.0053431382,0.032717396,-0.008998901,0.014745016,0.017596394,0.024934215,0.0014043503,0.01832126,0.043588202,-0.0016667427,0.0045865895,-0.0039267926,-0.016370129,-0.006734872,-0.0008298255,-0.012469767,-0.024551388,0.00826149,0.03368522,-0.027542323,0.02841509,0.006318104,-0.16053273,-0.0075541437,-0.018250268,-0.01434303,0.015601639,0.024562165,-0.010827295,-0.0029568267,0.021121418,-0.013738,-0.043642513,0.03798839,-0.042978503,0.0055590663,-0.0069434484,0.0031637184,0.02080225,-0.0020268096,0.022188582,-0