  ('brand_example', 'Clinical efficacy brand voice — ingredient-led, transparency-first tone (Drunk Elephant / The Ordinary pattern)', 'Drunk Elephant hero: "The Drunk Difference — Drunk Elephant believes performance and personality can live in the same jar. Skin-smart formulas developed with efficacious levels of active ingredients that can be easily absorbed and put to use." CTAs: "SHOP ALL SKIN CARE" (primary, all-caps filled button) + "LEARN MORE" (secondary text). The Ordinary: "CLINICAL WITH INTEGRITY." Key tone markers: specificity ("efficacious levels", "easily absorbed"), intellectual confidence, no lifestyle language, transparency-led positioning. Avoid discount language entirely in this voice. Secondary banner variation: "Discover In-Store Consultations — One-on-one consultations have arrived. Expert guidance tailored to your skin''s needs. Book Now / Learn More" — same pattern applied to service, dual CTA with same hierarchy. Use for educated beauty consumers who research formulations.', '{"applicable_when":"clinical, dermatology, and science-led brand hero and collection banners","category":"clinical_beauty","evidence_source":"Drive corpus — Drunk Elephant and The Ordinary banners 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[-0.009710539,-0.031693533,-0.013000689,-0.07694565,-0.023291608,0.0010761259,-0.00463807,-0.004892107,-0.0056718593,-0.037553392,-0.016862938,0.005941173,0.0076531894,-0.0048380233,0.12872301,-0.004183572,-0.007954595,-0.00280974,0.0068300217,-0.005501785,0.00082477456,0.0071446653,-0.0042244084,-0.0037316557,-0.009377497,-0.01140876,0.0005938953,0.023724634,0.022061748,-0.00543148,-0.00045221363,-0.0056757587,0.022654193,0.005103416,0.005638633,0.03904944,0.02365015,-0.01757145,0.014098057,0.009264619,-0.00583976,0.029135088,0.012884156,-0.0032954891,-0.01683281,-0.006118211,-0.0014333717,-0.03588928,-0.0020824843,0.017529588,-0.018193841,0.013705984,-0.002767215,-0.16453356,0.007925803,-0.008300891,0.007851965,-0.01736942,-0.0045288536,-0.010421163,-0.01