  ('brand_example', 'Luxury beauty brand voice — philosophical, identity-led, short declarative tone (WESSAINT AURENT pattern)', 'WESSAINT AURENT About banner: headline "ABOUT US", body "we believe that beauty is more than just skin deep. It''s a feeling of confidence, a reflection of self-care, and an expression.", CTA "DISCOVER MORE". Tone markers: lowercase brand copy despite all-caps brand name (deliberate contrast), philosophical framing ("more than just skin deep"), no product names, no prices, no discounts, open-ended CTA. The use of "an expression" as the final clause — a sentence fragment — is intentional; it leaves the thought open for the consumer to complete. This voice archetype is appropriate for brand introduction pages, About banners, and high-funnel awareness campaigns where the goal is emotional connection rather than immediate transaction.', '{"applicable_when":"premium and luxury brand hero and About section banners","category":"luxury_beauty","evidence_source":"Drive corpus — WESSAINT AURENT About Us banner 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[-0.018850736,-0.0023619374,0.002061002,-0.08847386,-0.018083861,-0.01408711,-0.020371322,-0.020113468,-0.010703665,-0.0003124296,-0.0014455959,0.014467679,-0.014115318,0.014142091,0.13891007,-0.00040931135,0.0015805523,0.016226966,0.008792178,0.0005363279,-0.0051060775,0.0016587271,-0.0084266,-0.018542292,-0.011930061,-0.014758554,0.005967776,0.020392297,0.028723268,-0.012791802,-0.01432162,-0.009301898,0.036990635,0.003977097,0.045354273,0.032574505,0.02093559,-0.043370713,0.019203573,0.037446503,0.002606743,-0.007842839,0.014371771,-0.0022829492,-0.0020128512,0.0024220606,-0.0031638374,-0.03295826,0.0169308,0.049325563,-0.0167533,-0.0011489597,0.004266127,-0.1564484,-0.012504035,0.0012766271,0.002162478,0.027335446,0.020101879,0.002829019,-0.02995509,0.015849452,-0.017477658,-0.052477043,0.032698154,-0.018432004,0.0004415668,-0.033781067,0.021359123,0.006161082,-0.01580978,-0.00859984,-0.005480528,-0.014012648,0.0108318