  ('brand_example', 'Product launch brand voice — availability-anchored, sensory-specific, lowercase CTA tone (Kylie Jenner Cosmetics pattern)', 'Kylie Jenner Cosmetics demonstrates three banner variants from the Drive corpus: (1) Launch badge: "NOW AVAILABLE / HYDRATING LIP ESSENTIALS / meet our new juicy, kiss-proof coconut water lip stain and nourishing, moisture-rich cloud balm. / shop now" with product pack shots. (2) Campaign concept: "HYDRATE, TINT, GO / discover two new limited-edition formulas for hydrated, juicy lips all summer long: coconut water lip stain delivers lasting comfort and up to 24-hour moisture / cloud balm offers instant hydration and doubles as a daily lip mask / shop now." (3) Seasonal: "THE SCENT OF THE SUMMER / a sweet, warm floral scent, our debut fragrance cosmic kylie jenner is perfect for summer. / shop now." Common markers: all-lowercase CTA "shop now", sensory adjectives ("juicy", "kiss-proof", "nourishing", "moisture-rich"), availability or scarcity cue ("NOW AVAILABLE", "limited-edition"), product-specific description. Brand name "KYLIE JENNER" in bold caps secondary to product line.', '{"applicable_when":"new product launches, limited-edition drops, seasonal collection introductions in beauty","category":"product_launch","evidence_source":"Drive corpus — Kylie Jenner Cosmetics lip and fragrance launch banners 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[-0.019316982,-0.007832456,0.012178312,-0.07035646,-0.01850494,-0.0074134716,-0.023539353,9.096631e-05,-0.010426768,-0.02238936,-0.011038122,-0.008288573,0.0049736206,0.010964548,0.13240892,0.036326345,-0.00048314448,0.005798914,0.008926029,0.009272424,-0.01262642,0.021732235,-0.021049824,-0.0063501936,-0.0053901672,-0.014075097,0.017205957,0.01180295,0.017339297,0.018695079,-0.011385739,0.0133113405,0.037475903,-0.020390468,0.0053681014,0.022502955,0.011199352,-0.015366275,0.00875135,0.015231949,0.0027308783,0.0021354419,0.026496137,-0.025649602,-0.0062879715,0.0066790646,0.0061105504,-0.02690169,-0.004