  ('seo_pattern', 'Canonical URL tag on collection and promotional pages prevents duplicate content from URL parameter variants', 'Collection pages accessed with faceted filter parameters (?color=red&sort=price_asc), UTM tracking (?utm_source=instagram), or pagination (?page=2) produce URL variants that Google may index as separate pages, splitting PageRank. The canonical tag tells crawlers which URL is authoritative. Shopify provides the canonical_url global variable which resolves to the clean canonical URL for all page types. Pattern: `<link rel="canonical" href="{{ canonical_url }}">` in the theme layout head. For banner agent-generated promotional pages, the canonical should point to the root collection URL, not the promotional URL, unless the page has unique content merit.', '{"applicable_when":"collection pages, promotional landing pages, faceted filter pages","category":"canonical","evidence_source":"Google Search Central canonical spec; Shopify canonical_url variable 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[-0.0025627522,0.003923856,-0.015923362,-0.080556974,-0.019976804,0.007309696,-0.028804947,0.0042443555,0.0041116006,-0.008221493,0.006277472,-0.0073554995,-0.004360064,0.0052641146,0.12826633,0.024893856,-0.00081812456,-0.003209114,0.012659542,-0.014952699,-0.00019556357,0.004888966,0.022968894,-2.5168845e-05,0.015172522,-0.009342395,0.025809826,-0.025051096,0.055363666,-0.005093071,-0.023028778,-0.015643332,0.03002585,-0.025246644,0.0007478831,0.019615635,0.010056915,-0.02082561,-0.0056668646,0.019501299,-0.005383973,0.023694793,0.016118607,-0.015460314,-0.0072961743,-0.0020460212,-0.0051295054,-0.026470048,-0.027868174,0.03815414,-0.02751572,0.010285979,0.0033076415,-0.17576206,-0.009333202,-0.020827938,-0.0010681043,0.010991222,-0.006387774,0.018721264,0.0018581146,2.7619786e-05,-0.007862218,-0.04559232,-0.009082677,0.0016799364,0.0145127205,-0.014499851,-0.015407824,0.014671999,0.0033423274,-0.0060252007,-0.011543048,-0.0090073105,-0.01071864,-0.026344344,0.034582537,0.