  ('seo_pattern', 'Descriptive image filenames and alt text make banner images indexable in Google Image Search', 'Beauty brands like Drunk Elephant, NaturaGlow, and Kylie Jenner generate significant discovery traffic via Google Image Search — shoppers searching for product images find the brand. Two factors control image indexability: the file name and the alt text. Shopify CDN serves images at URLs that include the original filename. Meaningful filenames: "naturaglow-body-wash-hero.jpg" outperforms "Screenshot 2026-05-29 at 8.21.37 p.m..png" for SEO. Alt text should describe the image content and include the product name: `alt="NaturaGlow Body Wash — nourishing soap on bathroom shelf"`. Banner agent should validate that uploaded images have descriptive alt text and flag filenames that are generic screenshot names from the Drive corpus.', '{"applicable_when":"all banner images uploaded to Shopify CDN","category":"image_seo","evidence_source":"Google Image Search guidelines; Drive corpus — beauty product image naming 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[-0.03303679,0.009580685,-0.02223564,-0.084178545,-0.01310172,0.0028566306,-0.02823295,-0.001272437,-0.0029721386,-0.031293403,-0.010597352,0.010570874,0.016605174,-0.0018084104,0.13625968,0.006684886,-0.020004023,0.0012489482,0.013698662,-0.03319361,0.0042251255,0.007804189,0.022453947,-0.018783323,0.008681039,-0.017399542,0.025845965,-0.007522165,0.0070535424,0.020445904,-0.019956928,-0.0168485,0.048006408,-0.005967386,0.03962755,0.028186347,0.009773801,-0.02637275,0.014800475,0.03707757,-0.011574658,0.015617173,0.023644438,-0.008695314,-0.005371843,-0.008497653,-0.016871266,-0.035126463,-0.0053061685,0.012111854,-0.027333248,0.024817288,-0.019365627,-0.15705483,0.0109864455,-0.02416135,0.00026274336,0.011191293,-0.0004503076,-0.007068039,-0.008071993,0.02046182,-0.012281927,-0.049966194,-0.010974783,-0.028621722,-0.00448169,-0.026328994,-0.00682737,0.0063558593,-0.0054571386,-0.007777637,-0.014483099,0.0055869506,0.0011260101,-0.0