  ('seo_pattern', 'Twitter Card meta tags for summary_large_image display the hero banner when shared on X (Twitter)', 'Kylie Jenner Cosmetics and similar beauty brands with strong Twitter/X presence benefit from summary_large_image cards that display the hero banner image prominently in the feed. Required tags: `<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">`, `<meta name="twitter:title" content="{{ page_title }}">`, `<meta name="twitter:description" content="{{ page.description | strip_html | truncate: 160 }}">`, `<meta name="twitter:image" content="{{ page_image | img_url: ''1200x630'', crop: ''center'' }}">`. Twitter image must be at least 1200×630px and under 5MB. When og:image is set, Twitter falls back to it — but explicit twitter:image tags allow a different image optimised for the 2:1 Twitter crop ratio.', '{"applicable_when":"all Shopify pages with hero banners for brands with an X/Twitter presence","category":"social_meta","evidence_source":"Twitter/X Card spec; Drive corpus — Kylie Jenner, Bearen social presence 2026-05"}'::jsonb, '[-0.02371609,0.004338919,-0.02127256,-0.08901303,-0.013956876,-0.0031587444,-0.022111943,0.016667563,-0.004457123,-0.019587345,-0.020987459,-0.001986935,0.0014118543,-2.6790965e-05,0.14567669,0.04237395,-0.017632898,-0.00026507015,0.0043475423,0.0058600456,-0.0001362556,0.0047144596,-0.005849278,-0.019821389,0.006239726,0.0044113537,0.010507868,-0.013380005,0.0040903357,0.031796984,-0.004305602,-0.0073676636,0.030091235,0.016310573,-0.008821458,0.032184526,0.021494387,-0.034853883,0.021838987,0.013792802,0.007239666,0.010799882,0.025498146,0.006573911,-0.011489015,0.01920539,-0.013527807,-0.004925958,-0.008834908,0.014647718,-0.04543621,0.014953156,-0.028396146,-0.15929055,-0.0006795542,-0.021708747,-0.0062698456,-0.0030269271,-0.02225551,0.0018852976,0.0014947656,0.025990851,0.022859868,-0.05391952,-0.014720682,-0.0058508674,0.001524917,-0.013366799,0.0023926352,-0.009494282,0.007866939,-0.014171391,-0.009665431,-0.